OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FChannel Islanders living in Dubai say
OL,7,Fthe past few days have been
OL,8,F'"petrifying" and "surreal" after
OL,9,Fbeing caught in the crossfire of
OL,10,Fmissile strikes taking place across
OL,11,Fthe Middle East.
OL,13,FThe United States and Israel launched
OL,14,Fairstrikes on major cities in Iran on
OL,15,FSaturday - prompting retaliation from
OL,16,FIran, who fired ballistic missiles and
OL,17,Fdrones at US assets and allies across
OL,18,Fthe region.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
