PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FSome of the countries targeted include
OL,7,FBahrain, Kuwait, Qatar, Jordan, and
OL,8,Fthe United Arab Emirates (UAE) - a
OL,9,Fpopular holiday destination where
OL,10,Fthousands of British expats currently
OL,11,Flive.
OL,13,FThese British nationals are now left
OL,14,Fstranded, as major airports in the
OL,15,Fregion remain closed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
