OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FRyan Hodgson - a Jersey man who moved
OL,7,Fhis family to Dubai in the UAE in
OL,8,FSeptember - describes the events of
OL,9,Fthe past 24 hours as "the sort of
OL,10,Fthing you never really think you're
OL,11,Fgoing to expect to experience".
OL,13,F"It's been surreal, petrifying", he
OL,14,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"24 hours ago, everything felt quite
OL,7,Fnormal - it was just a normal Saturday
OL,8,F- and then next thing we know we're
OL,9,Fseeing things in the sky that
OL,10,Fshouldn't be there, and then you go
OL,11,Fonto social media and see everything
OL,12,Fthat's happening in the world and then
OL,13,Fwe're getting advised 'you need to
OL,14,Fstay in the house'.
OL,16,F"It felt like we were in the middle of
OL,17,Fa warzone."
OL,19,FHis family live close to an airbase,
OL,20,Fand they spent the night watching and
OL,21,Flistening for missiles.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"Every hour throughout the night, it
OL,7,Ffelt like there was something flying
OL,8,Fover us - every hour on the hour -
OL,9,Fthat shouldn't be there.
OL,11,F"When you look outside you can see
OL,12,Fclear paths, if you like, of very
OL,13,Fclear smoke and there's a fire often
OL,14,Fwhere it's coming from", he describes.
OL,16,F"It's petrifying for us to see - this
OL,17,Fis really something that's designed to
OL,18,Fkill someone."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FRyan adds it's been difficult to try
OL,7,Fto explain to his young daughters what
OL,8,Fhas been going on without scaring them.
OL,10,FHowever, he says the family feels "as
OL,11,Frelatively safe as can be given the
OL,12,Fsituation", and feels the messaging
OL,13,Ffrom local authorities has been
OL,14,Freassuring - with the community centre
OL,15,Fnear his home opening for people to
OL,16,Fshelter in, and alerts on his phone
OL,17,Fproviding regular official updates.
OL,19,FIt means he isn't looking to leave the
OL,20,Fcountry anytime soon.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"You have to think this is an isolated
OL,7,Fthing that unfortunately has happened
OL,8,Fwhere we happen to be - it's not a
OL,9,Fregular occurance", he explains,
OL,10,Fadding that for his young children "it
OL,11,Fwould be more traumatic to try to jump
OL,12,Fship".
OL,14,F"I feel optimistic that the powers
OL,15,Fthat be are going to be able to try to
OL,16,Fresolve it relatively quickly."
OL,18,FIt's a sentiment echoed by Guernsey
OL,19,Fman Matthew Bougourd - an Estate Agent
OL,20,Fwho's been living in Dubai since 2024.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FHe says the strikes have been shocking
OL,7,F- and not the kind of thing he ever
OL,8,Fdreamed would happen when he made the
OL,9,Fdecision to move.
OL,11,F"Obviously you know when you're going
OL,12,Fto the Middle East, there's a lot of
OL,13,Fother countries in the area that are a
OL,14,Flittle bit more unstable - obviously
OL,15,FIran being one of them", Matthew
OL,16,Fexplains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"Fortunately for me being in the UAE,
OL,7,Fit's a very neutral country generally
OL,8,Fspeaking - so for me I've never felt
OL,9,Funsafe, never felt like anything like
OL,10,Fthis would happen."
OL,12,FHowever, he adds the experience hasn't
OL,13,Fmade him change his mind about living
OL,14,Fabroad.
OL,16,F"I think it's actually reinforced my
OL,17,Fliving decision - I know that's an odd
OL,18,Fthing to say in a situation like this.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"Just seeing how it's been dealt with
OL,7,F- the guidance has been clear, we all
OL,8,Fgot sent alerts on our phone the
OL,9,Fsecond it started and throughout the
OL,10,Fwhole process - so it's reinforced my
OL,11,Fbelief that being in this city, in
OL,12,Fthis country, is a good place to be",
OL,13,Fhe says.
OL,15,FHe adds he feels the weekend has been
OL,16,Feye-opening, saying it's shown him
OL,17,F"another part of the world (he)
OL,18,Fotherwise wouldn't be exposed to".
OL,26,@yD@\pmyD@_pn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
