PN,38711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FHowever, ITV News spoke to some
OL,7,FChannel Islanders living in the region
OL,8,Fwho didn't feel as safe sharing their
OL,9,Fthoughts after they were told others
OL,10,Fhad been arrested for doing so.
OL,12,FBoth Bailiwicks have issued official
OL,13,Fadvice encouraging anyone currently in
OL,14,Fthe Middle East - or with connections
OL,15,Fthere - to consult the latest updates
OL,16,Fissued by the UK Foreign, Commonwealth
OL,17,Fand Development Office (FCOD).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,FThis includes recommendations for
OL,7,Fthose in Bahrain, Kuwait, Qatar, the
OL,8,FUAE, and Oman to shelter in a secure
OL,9,Flocation.
OL,11,FPeople in the region are also
OL,12,Fencouraged to register their presence
OL,13,Fwith the UK government.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Lyndon Farnham,
OL,16,FJersey's Chief Minister, says:
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with everyone
OL,19,Faffected by the recent events in the
OL,20,FMiddle East.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"Many islanders have personal or
OL,7,Fprofessional connections to the
OL,8,Fregion, and they will naturally be
OL,9,Fconcerned for family, friends, and
OL,10,Fcolleagues.
OL,12,F"At a time of heightened uncertainty,
OL,13,Four priority is to ensure that those
OL,14,Fwho may be affected have access to
OL,15,Fclear, reliable information.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"The Government of Jersey continues to
OL,7,Fmonitor events closely through
OL,8,Festablished channels. We remain in
OL,9,Fregular contact with UK authorities
OL,10,Fand will provide further updates or
OL,11,Fsupport for islanders if it becomes
OL,12,Fnecessary".
OL,14,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,15,FLindsay de Sausmarez, says:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772568682
OL,3,C'It's surreal, petrifying': Channel
OL,4,CIslanders stranded in the Middle East
OL,6,F"In light of ongoing missile strikes
OL,7,Fin Iran and the neighbouring regions,
OL,8,Fislanders who are in the Middle East,
OL,9,For have friends and relatives there,
OL,10,Fare strongly advised to follow
OL,11,Fguidance issued by the UK FCOD.
OL,13,F"Nationals of other countries should
OL,14,Fconsult and follow advice provided by
OL,15,Ftheir respective governments."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
